{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/architecture/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"F&Y-BLOG","author":"kimifdw"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"af86eef2-15a1-5286-9cb7-0abbb79dbc41","html":"<h2 id=\"对技术架构的理解\"><a href=\"#%E5%AF%B9%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>对技术架构的理解</h2>\n<h3 id=\"顶层设计\"><a href=\"#%E9%A1%B6%E5%B1%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>顶层设计</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>要做什么事要定义的非常清楚，要达到什么样的结果也要定义的非常清楚</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"物理架构\"><a href=\"#%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>物理架构</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>独立</li>\n<li>连续性</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"应用架构\"><a href=\"#%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>应用架构</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>将单纯的代码共建模型抽象成横向和纵向的业务包模型，做到业务与业务隔离，业务与平台隔离</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"架构师的角色\"><a href=\"#%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>架构师的角色</h2>\n<h3 id=\"型散而神不散\"><a href=\"#%E5%9E%8B%E6%95%A3%E8%80%8C%E7%A5%9E%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A3\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>型散而神不散</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>用<strong>架构的意识</strong>解决实际的技术/业务问题</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"前瞻性\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E7%9E%BB%E6%80%A7\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前瞻性</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>大量的实践和知识积累</strong>，站在过去的肩膀上</li>\n<li><strong>接触更多的人和事，用新的方法解决新的问题</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"解决复杂问题\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解决复杂问题</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>基本面：高并发和高可用</li>\n<li>紧迫问题：用户体验、提升效率、低成本</li>\n<li>挑战：用户分层、内部技术人员增多</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"架构师需要的能力\"><a href=\"#%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%B8%88%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>架构师需要的能力</h2>\n<h3 id=\"发现问题\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>发现问题</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>看待问题。不要只看见眼前这一个问题，还要看见这个问题背后是什么，这一类问题背后是什么，我怎么能用抽象的方法解决一类问题</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"定义和分析问题\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%92%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义和分析问题</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>将发现的问题进行抽象和归纳，定义出问题的基本要素，同时定义出问题的短期和长期方案，推进技术的进步</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"解决问题\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解决问题</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>实施路径和解决方案，协同团队和上下游，推进问题的解决。</li>\n<li>\n<p>架构要解决的一定是一个全局问题</p>\n<ol>\n<li>沟通能力</li>\n<li>救火能力</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"架构师的挑战\"><a href=\"#%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%91%E6%88%98\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>架构师的挑战</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>全局式的视角</li>\n<li>技术广度。<strong>彻底了解透彻</strong>目前用到的技术，依赖于积累，带着问题去想。将<strong>知识形成体系</strong>，有能力去消化和打通不同技术点背后的相关性</li>\n<li>\n<p>持续学习。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>跟工作相关，体系化学习。</li>\n<li>去看论文。</li>\n<li>数据相关。OLTP 和 OLAP</li>\n<li>业务理解。跟业务结合，用不一样的思路解决实际的业务问题，带来更低的成本、更高的效率</li>\n<li>结果。协调更多的人。</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"架构师的工作模式\"><a href=\"#%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>架构师的工作模式</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>内部工作。思考和处理信息，团队中的沟通（50）</li>\n<li>内部沟通。必须了解很广泛的知识，包括倾听、阅读和问问题（25）</li>\n<li>对外沟通。信息传播，包括文档演示、写文档和提供支持（25）</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"异步传播\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%A0%E6%92%AD\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>异步传播</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>问题点：缺乏沟通</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>书面方式传播</li>\n<li>决策记录</li>\n<li>常规简报。每周给项目成员发一份简报</li>\n<li>具象化是一种通用的语言。让架构师承担起为具体的场景解释架构的职责。减少谈论大的概览。</li>\n</ol>","timeToRead":4,"frontmatter":{"title":"系统架构总结","date":"February 06, 2021","spoiler":"架构 感悟"},"fields":{"slug":"/architecture/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/architecture/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/jit/","directoryName":"jit"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Java即时编译器原理解析及实践"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/OLAP/","directoryName":"OLAP"},"frontmatter":{"title":"OLAP笔记"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["336482444"]}